    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Amazon Customer
    5 out of 5 stars
    Happy kids, happy parents
    Perfect for our 2 & 4 year olds during a long road trip! They each had an iPad and we didn't want the sound levels competing against the other or against our music & conversation. They wore them for almost 3 hours straight before we made them take a break from the iPads and never complained once. I did have to help them readjust on their heads a few times because they moved them around occasionally and didn't know where to put them to keep it in place. While testing the headphones out at home, the 2 year old was reluctant and wouldn't leave them on to even try it out. However, on the morning of our trip, as soon as I turned on Thomas the Train and put them on his head while buckled in, he was happy as can be. As for the sound, there is a volume limit, but it's plenty loud without me worrying about their ear drums. The size was great on the smallest setting for both and even fit me on the largest (I am petite so this probably wouldn't be the case for all adults). The purple/pink and aqua colors were great with no complaints from the kids.
